@baseURL = http://localhost:3000

### Retrieve all orders
GET {{baseURL}}/orders/all

### Retrieve all of a user's orders
GET {{baseURL}}/orders/user/{userId}

### Retrieve an order by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/orders/{id}

### Create a new order
